uble%20for%20Chinese%20fast-fashion%20brands%2C%20particularly%20Gen%20Z-favorite%20budget%20brands%20like%20Shein%20and%20Temu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mexico-canada-china-tariffs-january-20-trade-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintends%20to%20slap%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20additional%2010%25%20import%20tariff%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20any%20tariffs%20he%20already%20plans%20to%20impose.%20He%20said%20these%20tariffs%20were%20a%20punishment%20for%20China%20sending%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20amounts%20of%20drugs%2C%20in%20particular%20Fentanyl%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20term%2C%20from%202016%20to%202020%2C%20Trump%20imposed%20protectionist%20policies%2C%20including%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20%2450%20billion%20worth%20of%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-war-us-china-tariffs-lost-no-meaning-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20war%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20campaigning%20this%20year%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20impose%20tariffs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-reaction-donald-trump-election-victory-tariffs-trade-disputes-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E60%25%20or%20higher%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Chinese%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Trump's%20Monday%20statements%2C%20Chinese%20Embassy%20Spokesperson%20Liu%20Pengyu%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20will%20win%20a%20trade%20war%20or%20a%20tariff%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnrf.com%2Fresearch%2Festimated-impacts-proposed-tariffs-imports-apparel-toys-furniture-household-appliances%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20on%20November%204%20calculated%20that%20American%20consumers%20could%20lose%20between%20%2446%20billion%20and%20%2478%20billion%20in%20spending%20power%20yearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20imposes%20a%2010%25%20universal%20tariff%20on%20all%20imports%20and%20an%20additional%2060%25%20to%20100%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20China%2C%20apparel%20prices%20would%20increase%20between%2012.5%25%20and%2020.6%25%2C%20the%20NRF%20wrote%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20would%20cut%20back%20spending%20on%20apparel%20by%20up%20to%2033%25%2C%20the%20NRF%20report%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20cheap%20Chinese%20e-commerce%20businesses%3A%20Temu%20parent%20company%20PDD%20has%20for%20months%20warned%20of%20slowing%20profits.%20The%20company's%20stock%20is%20down%2031%25%20this%20year.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Shein%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20a%20hotly-anticipated%20initial%20public%20offering%2C%20likely%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Jacks%2C%20an%20economics%20professor%20from%20Singapore's%20Yale-NUS%20College%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20think%20of%20any%20scenario%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20fast-fashion%20industry%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20escapes%20revived%20US%20protectionism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20because%20their%20supply%20chains%20originate%20from%20China%2C%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20are%20%26quot%3Blikely%20to%20receive%20even%20greater%20scrutiny%20and%20suffer%20higher%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20other%20businesses%20that%20manufacture%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Morocco%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20will%20almost%20certainly%20pay%20higher%20prices%2C%20and%20producers%20will%20almost%20certainly%20earn%20lower%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacks%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20have%20not%20publicly%20addressed%20possible%20US%20tariffs%2C%20including%20on%20PDD's%20earnings%20call%20last%20week.%20Lei%20Chen%2C%20PDD's%20co-CEO%2C