%20economy%20about%20144%20billion%20rupees%20(%24518%20million)%20daily%2C%20according%20to%20finance%20minister%20Muhammad%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20release%2C%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20wants%20Sharif's%20government%20to%20reverse%20a%20new%20law%20that%20it%20says%20gives%20the%20government%20the%20power%20to%20interfere%20in%20judicial%20affairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732599120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Faqnqeokg_pakistan-protest_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-killed-as-thousands-of-imran-khans-supporters-clash-with-cops-in-pakistan-7107551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20army%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20%26quot%3Bshoot%20on%20sight%26quot%3B%20after%20clashes%20with%20demonstrators%20killed%20four%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20one%20protester%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-killed-as-thousands-of-imran-khans-supporters-clash-with-cops-in-pakistan-7107551%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poll%20Charges%20Dismissed%2C%20Trump%20Rips%20Into%20Democrats%20For%20Filing%20%26quot%3BFalse%20Cases%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20ripped%20into%20the%20Democrats%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20targeting%20him%20with%20false%20cases%20over%20political%20revenge.%20He%20claimed%20the%20government%20spent%20over%20%24100%20million%20to%20target%20him%20using%20state%20prosecutors%20and%20district%20attorneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20onli