s%20at%20the%20Taj%20Hotel%2C%20Oberoi%20Trident%20Hotel%2C%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Terminus%2C%20Leopold%20Cafe%2C%20Mumbai%20Chabad%20House%2C%20Nariman%20House%2C%20Cama%20Hospital%2C%20and%20Metro%20Cinema%20by%20ten%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20166%20people%2C%20including%2020%20security%20force%20personnel%20and%2026%20foreigners%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20300%20injured%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%202008.%20The%20ten%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20terrorists%20came%20to%20Mumbai%20via%20the%20sea%20route%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20carried%20out%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20President%20of%20India%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20leaders%20and%20citizens%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20are%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20166%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks.%20While%20the%20pain%20of%20that%20day%20remains%2C%20let%20us%20honour%20the%20heroes%20who%20risked%20their%20lives%20to%20save%20hundreds%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20five%20heroes%20who%20displayed%20remarkable%20courage%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETukaram%20Omble%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETukaram%20Omble%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20who%20was%20killed%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20city.%20Mr%20Omble%2C%20unarmed%2C%20was%20killed%20while%20he%20tried%20to%20capture%20terrorist%20Ajmal%20Kasab%20on%20the%20night%20of%20November%2026%2C%202008.%20He%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20Girgaum%20Chowpatty%20in%20south%20Mumbai%2C%20but%20not%20before%20Mr%20Omble%20had%20ensured%20that%20the%20terrorist%20was%20caught%20alive.%20Mr%20Ombale%20was%20unarmed%2C%20but%20he%20grappled%20with%20Kasab%20and%20held%20on%20to%20his%20rifle%2C%20allowing%20others%20to%20arrest%20him.%20Kasab%20fired%20several%20rounds%20before%20his%20arrest%2C%20and%20the%20constable%20died%20of%20bullet%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMajor%20Sandeep%20Unnikrishnan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Sandeep%20lost%20his%20life%20while%20battling%20the%20Pakistani%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20terrorists%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%20in%202008.Major%20Sandeep%20Unnikrishnan%20was%20leading%20a%20team%20of%20NSG%20commandos%20to%20flush%20out%20terrorists%20from%20the%20Taj%20Palace%20Hotel%20in%20Mumbai%20when%20he%20was%20fatally%20wounded.He%20was%20conferred%20the%20Ashok%20Chakra%2C%20the%20country's%20highest%20peacetime%20gallantry%20award%2C%20on%2026%20January%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMallika%20Jagad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallika%20Jagad%2C%20the%20banquet%20manager%20at%20the%20Taj%20Palace%20Hotel%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%2C%20acted%20swiftly%20to%20protect%20guests.%20She%20and%20her%20team%20locked%20the%20doors%2C%20turned%20off%20the%20lights%2C%20and%20asked%20everyone%20to%20sit%20quietly.%20Despite%20blasts%20and%20smoke%20causing%20panic%2C%20Mallika%20remained%20calm%2C%20reassuring%20guests%20and%20explaining%20the%20situation.%20As%20fear%20escalated%20with%20cries%20for%20help%2C%20she%20maintained%20composure%20until%20learning%20that%20the%20Army%20had%20arrived%20to%20assist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarambir%20Singh%20Kang%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20Manager%20of%20the%20Taj%20Hotel%20in%20Mumbai%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%2C%20Karambir%20Kang%2C%20faced%20a%20personal%20tragedy%20when%20his%20wife%20and%20sons%20were%20trapped%20inside%20and%20lost%20their%20lives.%20Yet%2C%20his%20strength%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20this%20disaster%2C%20and%20he%20continued%20to%20work%20day%20and%20night%20to%20help%20the%20staff%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20to%20save%20everyone.%20Though%20he%20was%20not%20present%20during%20the%20attack%20when%20it%20began