f%20separated%2C%20BI%20reporter%20Gabby%20Landsverk%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-melinda-gates-divorce-adult-children-difficulty-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20essay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20strangest%20moments%20in%20processing%20the%20divorce%20was%20realizing%20later%20that%20I%20felt%20proud%20of%20my%20parents%20for%20making%20the%20choice%20to%20split%20up%20and%20move%20on%20with%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20unsettling%20to%20recognize%20the%20whole%20life%20they%20have%20outside%20of%20their%20parenting%2C%20as%20individuals%20with%20their%20own%20struggles%2C%20flaws%2C%20needs%2C%20and%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftish-cyrus-purcell-divorce-from-billy-ray-tough-adult-kids-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732596649000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6745287eede4eeae39298061%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftish-cyrus-purcell-divorce-from-billy-ray-tough-adult-kids-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20couple%20divorced%20in%202022.%20They%20previously%20filed%20for%20divorce%20in%202010%20and%202013%2C%20but%20reconciled%20both%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftish-cyrus-purcell-divorce-from-billy-ray-tough-adult-kids-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clashes%20At%20Udaipur%20Palace%20Gates%20Over%20New%20Maharana's%20Face-Off%20With%20Cousin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUdaipur%20witnessed%20a%20row%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20on%20Monday%20af