us%20royal%20was%20Rana%20Pratap%2C%20who%20fought%20the%20Mughals%20in%20the%20battle%20of%20Haldi%20Ghati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20symbolic%20coronation%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20blessings%20from%20family%20deities%20--%20the%20Dhooni%20mata%20temple%20inside%20the%20city%20palace%20and%20the%20Ekling%20Shiv%20temple%20about%2050%20kilometres%20from%20Udaipur.%C2%A0But%20since%20both%20temples%20are%20run%20by%20the%20trust%2C%20he%20was%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20city%20palace.%C2%A0The%20administration%20had%20tried%20to%20persuade%20the%20Museum%20Trust%20to%20allow%20not%20the%20entire%20procession%2C%20but%20a%20few%20erstwhile%20nobles%20to%20accompany%20Vishwaraj%20Singh%20into%20the%20palace%20for%20darshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20trouble%2C%20the%20police%20had%20set%20up%20barricades%20and%20deployed%20additional%20personnel%20in%20the%20area%20around%20the%20city%20palace%20gates.%20But%20when%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20palace%2C%20his%20enraged%20supporters%20broke%20barricades%20and%20tried%20to%20get%20close%20to%20the%20city%20palace%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20that%20we%20see%20today%20is%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20told%20media%20persons.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20for%20your%20support.%20On%20one%20side%20are%20properties%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20traditions%20where%20we%20seek%20blessings.%20This%20is%20wrong%20as%20far%20as%20traditions%20and%20society%20norms%20are%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20generation%20of%20Mewar%20royals%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20legal%20dispute%20over%20palaces%2C%20temples%20and%20forts%20that%20are%20now%20run%20and%20managed%20by%20nine%20trusts.%20All%20these%20trusts%20are%20handled%20by%20the%20uncle%20and%20cousin%20of%20Vishvaraj%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20morning%2C%20the%20Maharana%20Mewar%20Charitable%20Trust%20published%20in%20the%20local%20newspapers%20that%20they%20would%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20enter%20the%20trust%20premises%20as%20they%20anticipated%20that%20this%20could%20be%20done%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20trespass%20on%20and%20damage%20trust%20properties.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20goes%20back%20to%201984%2C%20when%20the%20former%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar%20Bhagwat%20Singhji%20made%20his%20younger%20son%20Arvind%20Singh%20the%20director%20of%20the%20trusts%2C%20effectively%20ousting%20the%20elder%20son%20Mahendra%20Singh%20from%20the%20royal%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20stand-off%20continues%20in%20Udaipur%2C%20this%20is%20a%20royal%20row%20that's%20going%20to%20echo%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Lakes%20for%20some%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732596540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3u1e7f6_udaipur-palace-violence_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fclashes-at-udaipur-palace-gates-over-new-maharanas-face-off-with-cousin-7104723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Udaipur%20witnessed%20a%20row%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20on%20Monday%20after%20the%20coronation%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20as%20the%2077th%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Suspense%3A%20BJP%20Firm%20On%20D%20Fadnavis%2C%20Shinde%20Sena%20Cites%20Nitish%20Kumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20over%20who%20will%20become%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20the%20Mahayuti's%20mammoth%20victory%20in%20the%20state%20polls%20has%20entered%20its%20third%20day.%20The%20tenure%20of%20the%2014th%20state%20Assembly%20ends%20today%20and%20incumbent%20Eknath%20Shinde%20will%20resign%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20But%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20a%20final%20call%20on%20who%20will%20get%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20want%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20to%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20while%20Shiv%20Sena%20MLAs%20are%20rooting%20for%20Mr%20Shinde%20to%20continue.%20The%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20back%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%20The%20BJP%20has%20132%20MLAs%2C%20the%20Sena%20has%2057%20and%20the%20NCP%2041.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20BJP%20needs%20only%20one%20of%20its%20two%20allies%20to%20reach%20the%20magic%20figure%20of%20145%20in%20the%20288-member%20Assembly.%20This%20leaves%20Mr%20Shinde%20with%20few%20bargaining%20chips%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20brainstorms%20on%20who%20will%20get%20the%20big%20post%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Sena%20leaders%20had%20planned%20to%20gather%20outside%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20bungalow%2C%20Varsha%2C%20apparently%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20for%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20But%20the%20Sena%20chief%20intervened%20and%20asked%20them%20not%20to.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20great%20victory%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliance%2C%20our%20government%20will%20be%20formed%20once%20again%20in%20the%20state.%20As%20a%20grand%20alliance%2C%20we%20contested%20the%20election%20together%20and%20are%20still%20together%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BOut%20of%20love%20for%20me%2C%20some%20people%20have%20appealed%20to%20everyone%20to%20gather%20together%20and%20come%20to%20Mumbai.%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20for%20your%20love.%20But%20I%20appeal%20that%20no%20one%20should%20come%20together%20in%20my%20support%20in%20such%20a%20manner.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESena%20Leader%20Refers%20To%20'Bihar%20Model'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20suspense%2C%20Sena%20spokesperson%20Naresh%20Mhaske%20cited%20the%20'Bihar%20model'%20to%20assert%20that%20Eknath%20Shinde%20should%20continue%20as%20chief%20minister%20even%20though%20BJP%20holds%20more%20seats%20in%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20Shinde%20should%20be%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20just%20like%20in%20Bihar%20where%20BJP%20did%20not%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20but%20still%20made%20JD(U)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%20the%20CM.%20Senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20(in%20Maharashtra)%20will%20ultimately%20take%20a%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mhaske%20told%20reporters%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mhaske%20also%20cited%20the%20Haryana%20example%20where%20the%20BJP%20stuck%20to%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Pravin%20Darekar%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20people%20had%20given%20a%20mandate%20to%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20stood%20behind%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20Fadnavis%20should%20become%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Maharashtra%20needs%20an%20astute%20and%20academic%20leader.%20He%20kept%20the%20alliance%20united%2C%20gave%20our%20allies%20candidates%2C%20and%20even%20stepped%20back%20when%20required.%20He%20has%20always%20maintained%20coordination%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLC%20said.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20pushing%20for%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20for%20the%20top%20post%20and%20any%20other%20decision%20would%20demoralise%20the%20party%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%2C%20which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20its%20Maharashtra%20victory%2C%20also%20favours%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20MLA%20from%20Nagpur%20South-West.%20The%20RSS%20will%20be%20celebrating%20its%20centenary%20next%20year%20and%20wants%20a%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%202019%20Repeat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Maharashtra%20polls%2C%20long%20term%20allies%20BJP%20and%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%20105%20and%20