e%20Festival%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20in%20October.%20Following%20this%20performance%2C%20she%20showcased%20her%20vocal%20prowess%20as%20the%20featured%20soloist%20in%20%E2%80%98Mahabharata%20%E2%80%93%20Mantras%2C%20Fights%2C%20and%20Threnody%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20opera%20by%20Riccardo%20Nova%2C%20performed%20with%20the%20Ensemble%20MusikFabrik%20in%20Florence%2C%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20she%20released%20her%20eponymous%20original%20album%20%E2%80%98VARI%E2%80%99.%20The%20album%20was%20produced%20by%20Grammy%20Award-winning%20artist%20Michael%20League%20of%20Snarky%20Puppy%20and%20features%20collaborations%20with%20legends%20like%20Victor%20Wooten%2C%20Hamilton%20De%20Holanda%2C%20Anat%20Cohen%2C%20and%20B%C3%A9la%20Fleck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20at%20the%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20Festival%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20along%20with%20other%20musicians.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet