e%22%3A%22IPL's%20Youngest%20Buy%20Suryavanshi%20Faces%20Age%20Fraud%20Allegations.%20Father%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sanjiv%20Suryavanshi%20sold%20his%20farmland%20to%20fund%20his%2010-year-old%20son%20Vaibhav's%20cricketing%20aspirations%2C%20little%20did%20he%20know%20that%20within%20three%20years%20the%20boy%20would%20be%20scripting%20history.%20During%20the%20second%20and%20final%20day%20of%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%20in%20Jeddah%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20at%2013%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20became%20the%20youngest%20cricketer%20ever%20to%20be%20picked%20by%20a%20franchise%20as%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20bought%20him%20for%20Rs%201.10%20crore.%20Sanjiv%2C%20who%20owned%20farmland%20in%20his%20native%20Motipur%20village%20which%20is%2015%20km%20from%20Samastipur%20town%20in%20Bihar%2C%20was%20lost%20for%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EWoh%20ab%20sirf%20humra%20bituwa%20nahi%20pura%20Bihar%20ka%20bituwa%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20is%20not%20just%20my%20son%20now%20but%20entire%20Bihar's%20son)%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjiv%20told%20PTI%20over%20phone%20as%20his%20son%20is%20currently%20in%20Dubai%20for%20the%20U-19%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20has%20worked%20hard.%20At%20the%20age%20of%208%20years%2C%20he%20excelled%20at%20U-16%20district%20trials.%20I%20would%20take%20him%20for%20his%20cricket%20coaching%20to%20Samastipur%20and%20then%20take%20him%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20the%20days%20of%20hardships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20were%20his%20finances%20in%20place%20as%20cricket%20is%20an%20investment%3F%20%26quot%3BNot%20just%20investment%2C%20it's%20a%20big%20investment.%20%3Cem%3EAapko%20kya%20bataye%20humne%20toh%20apna%20zameen%20tak%20bech%20diya.%20Abhi%20bhi%20halat%20pura%20sudhra%20nahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20have%20sold%20my%20land.%20Financial%20issues%20are%20still%20there).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20controversies%20regarding%20Vaibhav's%20actual%20age%20which%20many%20believe%20is%2015%20years%2C%20the%20father%20was%20quick%20to%20clarify.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20was%208%20and%20half%20years%20old%20he%20first%20appeared%20for%20a%20BCCI%20bone%20test.%20He%20has%20already%20played%20India%20U-19.%20We%20don't%20fear%20anyone.%20He%20can%20again%20undergo%20age%20test%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20sounded%20defiant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjiv%20said%20that%20Bihar%20Cricket%20Association%20president%20Rakesh%20Tiwary's%20%26quot%3Bblessings%26quot%3B%20have%20always%20helped%20Vaibhav%20in%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ERakesh%20ji%20ka%20ashirwaad%20raha%20hai%20bahoot%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rakesh%20ji's%20blessings%20are%20there).%26quot%3B%20His%20base%20price%20in%20the%20auction%20was%20Rs.%2030%20lakh%20and%20Delhi%20Capitals%20made%20the%20opening%20bid.%20RR%20entered%20the%20fray%20at%20Rs.%2035%20lakh%20and%20eventually%20got%20the%20better%20of%20DC%20to%20get%20the%20player%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20this%20bidding%20war%20happened%3F%20%26quot%3BRajasthan%20Royals%20had%20called%20him%20for%20trials%20in%20Nagpur.%20Vikram%20Rathour%20sir%20(batting%20coach)%20gave%20a%20match%20situation%20where%20he%20had%20to%20score%2017%20in%20an%20over.%20Bituwa%20ne%203%20chakka%20mara.%20%3Cem%3ETrials%20mein%20aat%20chakka%20aur%20char%20chauwaa%20mara%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20smashed%20three%20sixes.%20At%20trials%2C%20he%20hit%20eight%20sixes%20and%20four%20fours)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20father%20claimed%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%2013-year-old%2C%20it%20can%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20understand%20what%20it%20means%20to%20earn%20a%20crore.%20So%20how%20does%20he%20plan%20to%20keep%20his%20young%20son%20away%20from%20monetary%20discussions%3F%20%26quot%3BHe%20just%20wants%20to%20play%20cricket%20and%20nothing%20else.%20A%20few%20years%20back%20he%20loved%20Doremon%2C%20not%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjiv%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCA%20lauds%20selection%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCA%20president%20Tiwary%20was%20all%20praise%20for%20the%20prodigy%20after%20his%201.10%20crore%20bid%20for%20RR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVaibhav%20Suryavanshi's%20incredible%20achievement%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age%20fills%20us%20with%20immense%20pride%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiwary%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20journey%20from%20Bihar%20to%20the%20IPL%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20his%20talent%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20determination.%20The%20Bihar%20Cricket%20Association%20has%20always%20believed%20in%20nurturing%20young%20talent%2C%20and%20Vaibhav's%20success%20highlights%20the%20cricketing%20potential%20in%20our%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20confident%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20shine%20and%20inspire%20aspiring%20cricketers%20across%20Bihar%20and%20beyond.%20I%20congratulate%20Vaibhav%20and%20his%20family.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732584780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fo2ieshvo_vaibhav-suryavanshi_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-historys-youngest-buy-vaibhav-suryavanshi-13-faces-age-fraud-allegations-father-responds-7105193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20second%20and%20final%20day%20of%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%20in%20Jeddah%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20at%2013%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20became%20the%20youngest%20cricketer%20ever%20to%20be%20picked%20by%20a%20franchise%20as%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20bought%20him%20for%20Rs%201.10%20crore%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fipl-historys-youngest-buy-vaibhav-suryavanshi-13-faces-age-fraud-allegations-father-responds-7105193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mike%20Waltz%20to%20resign%20for%20national%20security%20role%20as%20Trump%20pushes%20Florida%20lawmakers%20to%20run%20for%20Congress%22%2C%22content%