C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f1705ecfb7f307e573d5a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221451%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20announced%20sweeping%20import%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20China.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20sweeping%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20on%20goods%20from%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20he%20plans%20to%20impose%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20announced%20his%20plan%20to%20slap%20an%20additional%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20goods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20announced%20a%20slate%20of%20tariffs%20that%20will%20hit%20the%20US's%20closest%20neighbors%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20pair%20of%20Truth%20Social%20posts%20on%20Monday%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20kick%20off%20his%20term%20on%20January%2020%20with%20executive%20orders%20%26quot%3Bto%20charge%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20a%2025%25%20Tariff%20on%20ALL%20products%20coming%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20its%20ridiculous%20Open%20Borders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Tariff%20will%20remain%20in%20effect%20until%20such%20time%20as%20Drugs%2C%20in%20particular%20Fentanyl%2C%20and%20all%20Illegal%20Aliens%20stop%20this%20Invasion%20of%20our%20Country!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20added%20that%20he%20believes%20both%20countries%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20right%20and%20power%26quot%3B%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20stop%20migrants%20from%20crossing%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hereby%20demand%20that%20they%20use%20this%20power%2C%20and%20until%20such%20time%20that%20they%20do%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20them%20to%20pay%20a%20very%20big%20price!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Monday%2C%20Trump%20also%20said%20he%20intends%20to%20slap%20China%20with%20an%20additional%2010%25%20import%20tariff%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20any%20tariffs%20he%20already%20plans%20to%20impose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tariffs%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20are%20because%20China's%20to%20blame%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20massive%20amounts%20of%20drugs%2C%20in%20particular%20Fentanyl%2C%20being%20sent%20into%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20long%20scrutinized%20China's%20role%20in%20the%20fentanyl%20supply%20chain%20and%20its%20role%20in%20the%20ongoing%20opioid%20crisis.%20A%202020%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Administration%20report%2C%20for%20one%2C%20identified%20China%20as%20a%20%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3Bprimary%20source%20of%20fentanyl%20and%20fentanyl-related%20substances%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20DEA%20said%20came%20through%20the%20mail%20and%20commercial%20cargo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20a%20congressional%20committee%20accused%20China%20of%20fueling%20the%20fentanyl%20crisis%20by%20helping%20to%20manufacture%20materials%20used%20in%20making%20the%20drug.%20Then%20in%20August%2C%20the%20Chinese%20government%20said%20it%20was%20imposing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2024-08-06%2Fdetail-inchsfmn0287678.d.html%3Fvt%3D4%26cid%3D76675%26node_id%3D76675%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20regulations%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Bprecursor%26quot%3B%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20previously%20said%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20impose%2060%25%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods.%20If%20Trump%20goes%20through%20with%20his%20earlier%20proposal%2C%20this%20additional%2010%25%20tariff%20will%20bring%20that%20percentage%20up%20to%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20what%20China's%20response%20to%20this%20new%20era%20of%20Trump%20