ng%20system%20has%20been%20hit%20with%20a%20ransomware%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20coffee%20company%20issued%20guidance%20for%20workers%20about%20how%20to%20handle%20pay%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20outage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20outage%20at%20Blue%20Yonder%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20software%2C%20also%20impacted%20grocery%20stores%20and%20Fortune%20500%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20company%20behind%20Starbucks'%20payment%20and%20scheduling%20system%C2%A0has%20been%20experiencing%20a%20dayslong%20ransomware%20attack%2C%20causing%20outages%20that%20are%20disrupting%20employee%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Blue%20Yonder%2C%20the%20company%20that%20makes%20the%20software%2C%20began%20on%20November%2021%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20caused%20outages%20in%20Starbucks's%20system%20for%20tracking%20employee%20hours%20and%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Starbucks%20has%20issued%20guidance%20to%20its%20employees%20about%20how%20to%20handle%20pay%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20Blue%20Yonder%20outage.%20Starbucks%20told%20its%20employees%20that%20payment%20for%20the%20period%20ending%20on%20November%2017%20would%20be%20unaffected%2C%20but%20there%20may%20be%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20following%20pay%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20ensure%20partners%20who%20receive%20less%20than%20their%20worked%20hours%20or%20intended%20sick%20and%2For%20vacation%20time%20will%20be%20paid%20correctly%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20internal%20documents%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outage%20has%20forced%20employees%20to%20track%20their%20shifts%20using%20pens%20and%20paper%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20viewed%20by%20BI%20indicate%20that%20employees%20who%20are%20missing%20pay%20from%20their%20checks%20should%20notify%20their%20store%20managers%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Any%20underpayme