quests%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20said%20the%20unanimous%20provision%20provides%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%26quot%3B%20and%20definitive%20response%20to%20grant-seekers%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20say%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20something%20that%20would%20ever%20receive%20my%20brother's%20consent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20said%20the%20clause%20isn't%20a%20remedy%20for%20all%20families%2C%20as%20it%20wouldn't%20work%20for%20a%20large%20group%20of%20children%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20remove%20the%20children's%20responsibility%20to%20choose%20where%20to%20donate%20billions.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20it%20would%20help%20improve%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20people%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20%24150%20billion%20net%20worth%2C%20Forbes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fprofile%2Fwarren-buffett%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Along%20with%20Melinda%20French%20Gates%20and%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20Buffett%20founded%20the%20Giving%20Pledge%2C%20a%20commitment%20for%20the%20world's%20billionaires%20to%20give%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20wealth%20towards%20philanthropy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20reiterated%20his%20philanthropic%20philosophy%20in%20the%20letter%20highlighting%20his%20children's%20growth%20into%20%26quot%3Bgood%20and%20productive%20citizens.%26quot%3B%20He%20joins%20a%20number%20of%20other%20business%20leaders%2C%20like%20Bill%20Gates%20and%20Michael%20Bloomberg%2C%20who%20prioritize%20philanthropy%20over%20solely%20allocating%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftycoons-not-leaving-money-to-their-kids-2013-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efortunes%20to%20their%20heirs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-advice-parents-planning-their-inheritance-will-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%