6quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fsocial%2Fpopular-youtuber-joe-rogan-wants-this-job-from-elon-musk-says-i-will-tell-the-same-lie%2Farticleshow%2F115662830.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Schools%20Asked%20To%20Move%20To%20%26quot%3BHybrid%20Mode%26quot%3B%20After%20Top%20Court's%20Observations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Monday%20directed%20government%2C%20private%20and%20civic%20body-run%20schools%20to%20conduct%20classes%20in%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%20mode%26quot%3B%20-%20online%20and%20offline%20-%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20after%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20announced%20relaxations%20under%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20to%20mitigate%20educational%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20poor%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20schools%20in%20the%20NCR%20had%20shifted%20to%20online%20lessons%20on%20October%2018%20amid%20a%20deterioration%20in%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20area.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20CAQM%20to%20consider%20restarting%20physical%20classes%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20noting%20many%20students%20lacked%20mid-day%20meals%20and%20infrastructure%20to%20attend%20online%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClause%2011%20of%20GRAP%20Stage-III%2C%20Clause%205%20of%20GRAP%20Stage-IV%20and%20Clause%208%20of%20GRAP%20Stage-IV%20(to%20the%20extent%20it%20relates%20to%20colleges%2C%20educational%20institutions)%20are%20relaxed%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20State%20Govts%20in%20the%20NCR%20and%20GNCTD%20shall%20ensure%20that%20all%20classes%20upto%2012th%20Standard%20in%20schools%20and%20those%20in%20colleges%2Feducational%20institutions%20are%20conducted%20in%20a%20'hybrid'%20mode%2C%20i.e%2C%20both%20in%20'physical'%20and%20also%20in%20an%20'online'%20mode%2C%20wherever%20online%20mode%20is%20feasible%2C%20in%20the%20territorial%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20and%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20Faridabad%2C%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Gautam%20Buddh%20Nagar%20in%20the%20NCR.%20The%20option%20to%20exercise%20online%20mode%20of%20education%2C%20wherever%20available%2C%20shall%20vest%20with%20the%20students%20and%20their%20guardians%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20(DoE)%2C%20Government%20of%20Delhi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20all%20Heads%20of%20Schools%20of%20Govt%2C%20Govt.%20Aided%2C%20Unaided%20Recognized%20Private%20Schools%20of%20DoE%2C%20NDMC%20(New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation)%2C%20MCD%20(Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi)%20and%20Delhi%20Cantonment%20Board%20are%20directed%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20of%20the%20above%20orders%20with%20immediate%20effect%20until%20further%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20CAQM%20permitted%20educational%20institutions%20to%20operate%20classes%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%26quot%3B%20format%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20attend%20either%20in%20person%20or%20online.%20%26quot%3BAll%20classes%20up%20to%2012th%20standard%20in%20schools%20and%20those%20in%20colleges%2Feducational%20institutions%20are%20to%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20'Hybrid'%20mode%2C%20i.e.%2C%20both%20in%20'physical'%20and%20'online'%20mode%2C%20wherever%20online%20mode%20is%20feasible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CAQM%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20came%20hours%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-to-reopen-top-court-says-many-dont-have-air-purifier-mid-day-meal-7102100%5C%22%3ECAQM%20to%20review%20GRAP%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20light%20of%20their%20impact%20on%20education.%20The%20court%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20prioritise%20education%20while%20raising%20several%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20number%20of%20students%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20the%20facility%20of%20mid-day%20meals%20as%20schools%20and%20anganwadis%20are%20closed.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20students%20do%20not%20have%20the%20facilities%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20online%20education.%20Many%20educational%20institutions%20do%20not%20have%20the%20facilities%20to%20provide%20online%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20court%20observed%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20residences%20of%20many%20students%20do%20not%20have%20air%20purifiers%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20there%20may%20not%20be%20any%20difference%20between%20children%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20those%20attending%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20remained%20alarming%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20the%20Capital's%2024-hour%20average%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20reading%20soaring%20to%20349%20from%20318%20the%20previous%20day%2C%C2%A0according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board's%204pm%20bulletin.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732559400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F8h6ncbp8_delhi-schools_625x300_01_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-asked-to-move-to-hybrid-mode-after-supreme-court-observations-7105038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Monday%20directed%20government%2C%20private%20and%20civic%20body-run%20schools%20to%20conduct%20classes%20in%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%20mode%26quot%3B%20-%20online%20and%20offline%20-%20after%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20announced%20relaxations%20under%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-schools-asked-to-move-to-hybrid-mode-after-supreme-court-observations-7105038%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Calls%20For%20US%20To%20Replace%20Fighter%20Jets%20With%20Drones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20tapped%20by%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20slash%20federal%20government%20spending%2C%20lashed%20out%20at%20modern%20fighter%20jets%20on%20Monday%2C%20saying%20that%20drones%20were%20the%20future%20of%20air%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManned%20fighter%20jets%20are%20obsolete%20in%20the%20age%20of%20drones%20anyway.%20Will%20just%20get%20pilots%20killed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20head%20of%20SpaceX%2C%20Tesla%20and%20X%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20singled%20out%20the%20F-35%20--%20a%20next-generation%20fighter%20jet%20manufactured%20by%20US-based%20Lockheed%20Martin%20that%20entered%20service%20in%202015%20--%20for%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20some%20idiots%20are%20still%20building%20manned%20fighter%20jets%20like%20the%20F-35%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%2C%20alongside%20a%20video%20of%20hundreds%20of%20drones%20hovering%20in%20formation%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%2C%20the%20world's%20most%20advanced%20fighter%2C%20is%20stealth%20capable%20and%20can%20also%20be%20used%20to%20gather%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%2C%20Poland%2C%20Finland%20and%20Romania%20have%20all%20recently%20signed%20deals%20for%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20development%2C%20however%2C%20has%20suffered%20from%20issues%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20design%20of%20its%20computer%20programs%2C%20and%20its%20very%20high%20operating%20costs%20are%20regularly%20criticized%20by%20its%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20F-35%20design%20was%20broken%20at%20the%20requirements%20level%2C%20because%20it%20was%20required%20to%20be%20too%20many%20things%20to%20too%20many%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Musk%20on%20Monday%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20expensive%20(and)%20complex%20jack%20of%20all%20trades%2C%20master%20of%20none.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mauro%20Gilli%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Swiss%20Federal%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Zurich%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20makes%20the%20F-35...%20expensive%20is%20the%20software%20and%20the%20electronics%2C%20not%20the%20pilot%20per%20se.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20significant%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20a%20reusable%20drone%20would%20need%20to%20get%20all%20that%20flashy%20electronics%20of%20an%20F-35%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20F-35%20had%20forced%20US%20rivals%20to%20develop%20their%20own%20aircraft%20and%20advanced%20radar%20to%20match%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20simply%20existing%2C%20the%20F-35%20and%20the%20B-1%20force%20Russia%20and%20China%20into%20strategic%20choices%20they%20would%20not%20have%20to%20make%20otherwise%20(i.e.%20budget%20allocations)%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilli%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20B-1%20heavy%20bomber%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20Musk%20were%20right%20(and%20he%20is%20not)%2C%20deleting%20the%20programs%20would%20relax%20these%20constraints%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732559280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F04dtmd6g_elon-musk_625x300_22_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-get-pilots-killed-elon-musk-calls-for-us-to-replace-fighter-jets-with-drones-7105091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20tapped%20by%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20slash%20federal%20government%20spe