y%20lower%20rates%2C%20with%200.8%20and%200.6%20victims%20per%20100%2C000%20people%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20male%20homicides%20happen%20outside%20of%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20men%20and%20boys%20account%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20homicide%20victims%2C%20women%20and%20girls%20continue%20to%20be%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20lethal%20violence%20in%20the%20private%20sphere%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20estimated%2080%25%20of%20all%20homicide%20victims%20in%202023%20were%20men%20while%2020%25%20were%20women%2C%20but%20lethal%20violence%20within%20the%20family%20takes%20a%20much%20higher%20toll%20on%20women%20than%20men%2C%20with%20almost%2060%25%20of%20all%20women%20who%20were%20intentionally%20killed%20in%202023%20being%20victims%20of%20intimate%20partner%2Ffamily%20member%20homicide%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fun-killing-women-girls-partners-family-global-c2f26290b8158e1d97b1b16ef76e85a8%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20steps%20being%20taken%20to%20prevent%20the%20killing%20of%20women%2C%20the%20killings%20%26quot%3Bremain%20at%20alarmingly%20high%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20emphasises%20that%20domestic%20violence%20is%20a%20preventable%20crime%2C%20often%20resulting%20from%20repeated%20episodes%20of%20gender-based%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20agencies%20urge%20countries%20to%20take%20timely%20and%20effective%20interventions%20to%20prevent%20domestic%20violence%20and%20protect%20women%20and%20girls%20from%20lethal%20violence%20in%20the%20private%20sphere.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732554000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F62u8irmg_femicide-reuters_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C