ia.com%2F341951%2Fratan-tata-trust-small-animal-hospital-veterinary-dogs-cats-pets-mumbai-mahalaxmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolutions%20for%20pet%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20came%20across%20wearables%20that%20functioned%20primarily%20as%20trackers.%20Driven%20by%20our%20personal%20needs%20for%20our%20own%20pets%2C%20we%20delved%20deeply%20into%20the%20animal%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20searching%20for%20predictive%20and%20preventive%20management%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Vani%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20emergencies%2C%20like%20Bruno%E2%80%99s%2C%20made%20Vivek%20and%20Vani%20realise%20the%20need%20for%20devices%20that%20could%20monitor%20a%20pet%E2%80%99s%20vitals%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20how%20humans%20track%20their%20blood%20pressure%2C%20oxygen%20levels%2C%20or%20blood%20sugar.%20When%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20reliable%20solutions%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20duo%20decided%20to%20create%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20they%20founded%20VETiNSTANT%2C%20an%20animal%20healthcare%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20an%20innovative%20platform%20for%20pet%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20real%20work%20began%20in%202021%2C%20when%20they%20launched%20the%20venture%20as%20a%20bootstrapped%20initiative%20using%20their%20own%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202021%2C%20we%20began%20designing%20an%20Apple-esque%20platform%20comprising%20a%20bed%2C%20bowl%2C%20and%20collar.%20The%20bed%20was%20intended%20to%20measure%20weight%20and%20sync%20the%20data%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20the%20bowl%20to%20monitor%20food%20and%20water%20intake%2C%20and%20the%20collar%20to%20track%20vital%20signs%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20we%20presented%20t