ndly-pet-products-india-collaborations-animal-welfare-artisan-crafts-yoda-pfa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%20for%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20us%20to%20develop%20Exam%20D.%20This%20product%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20features%20a%20graphical%20user%20interface%20that%20simplifies%20customer%20interaction.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20tested%20our%20prototypes%20in%20specific%20markets%20to%20validate%20usage%2C%20gather%20data%2C%20and%20gain%20acceptance%20from%20both%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20Exam%20D%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20VETiNSTANT%20app%20is%20downloaded%20from%20the%20App%20Store%20or%20Play%20Store%2C%20users%20are%20asked%20to%20add%20their%20profile%20details%20followed%20by%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20details%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20are%20one%20or%20many%20and%20what%20species%20they%20belong%20to.%20Users%20can%20buy%20the%20device%20from%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20Exam%20D.%20One%20measures%20temperature%20and%20performs%20heart%2C%20lung%20and%20abdomen%20auscultation%2C%20and%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%206%2C500%20(inclusive%20of%20taxes).%20The%20other%20performs%20all%20the%20above%20but%20also%20gives%20pet%20owners%20readings%20for%20SpO2%20and%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20costs%20Rs%209%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20only%20need%20to%20pair%20the%20app%20and%20device%20the%20first%20time%20when%20you%20buy%20the%20device.%20After%20that%2C%20all%20information%20presented%20in%20an%20executive%20summary%20will%20be%20available%20as%20a%20user%20goes%20through%20the%20prompts%20of%20the%20app%20and%20device%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20user%20interface%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K%20Rajkumar%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Veterinary%20Clinical%20Complex%20at%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20and%20Animal%20Sciences%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20is%20very%20convenient%2C%20especially%20for%20pet%20owners.%20They%20can%20easily%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20lung%20(respiratory)%20sounds%20by%20simply%20placing%20it%20near%20the%20animal.%20The%20recorded%20data%20can%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20a%20veterinarian%20through%20telemedicine%20for%20further%20analysis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exam%20D%20device%20developed%20by%20Vetinstant%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787.jpg%20767w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20them%20about%20two%20years%20and%20four%20prototypes%20to%20arrive%20at%20their%20final%20product%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%20with%20our%20VETiNSTANT%20tracker%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20device%2C%20we%20can%20accurately%20diagnose%20a%20pet%E2%80%99s%20condition%20using%20the%20recorded%20cardiac%20and%20lung%20sounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20key%20advantage%2C%20particularly%20for%20dogs%2C%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20non-invasive.%20Unlike%20rectal%20thermometers%2C%20which%20require%20regular%20sterilisation%2C%20Exam%20D%20offers%20a%20more%20comfortable%20alternative.%20Such%20devices%20are%20not%20yet%20available%20in%20India%2C%20so%20when%20the%20project%20proposal%20to%20standardise%20this%20equipment%20came%20to%20us%2C%20I%20was%20very%20excited.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20vets%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20introduced%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%20Pro%E2%80%99%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20busy%20professionals%20on%20the%20go.%20It%20enables%20instant%20tracking%20of%20multiple%20vitals%20and%20provides%20quicker%20access%20to%20data%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20tracks%20multiple%20metrics%20that%20vets%20are%20trained%20to%20interpret%2C%20such%20as%20murmur%20identification%20and%20grading%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20heart%20conditions%2C%20lung%20abnormalities%2C%20and%20insights%20into%20issues%20like%20COPD%2C%20asthma%2C%20and%20wheezing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20provides%20trend%20analytics%2C%20continuous%20care%20insights%20for%20proactive%20health%20monitoring%2C%20and%20ECG%20readings%20to%20detect%20heart%20irregularities.%E2%80%9D%20Exam%20D%20Pro%20was%20launched%20alongside%20Exam%20D%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20on%20board%20medical%20professionals%20and%20developed%20a%20digitised%20system%20called%20PAWS%20(Pets%20Administration%20and%20Workflow%20System)%20for%20pet%20parents%20and%20veterinary%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20system%2C%20pet%20parents%20can%20directly%20connect%20with%20their%20vets.%20Vani%20said%20in%20a%20past%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20device%2C%20there%20is%20an%20app%20that%20connects%20with%20the%20SaaS%20solution%20that%20the%20vet%20has.%20He%20has%20an%20app%20version%2C%20so%20he%20has%20data%20at%20his%20fingertips.%20All%20the%20data%20goes%20in%20a%20click%20of%20a%20button%20to%20the%20vet.%20They%20can%20set%20up%20calls%20online%20or%20offline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDCZF9okIh6V%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20VETiNSTANT%20(%40vetinstant)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20vets%2C%20PAWS%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20system%20to%20digitise%20the%20veterinary%20clinic%20from%20end%20to%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vani.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20not%20only%20takes%20care%20of%20billing%2C%20stock%20management%2C%20queuing%20systems%20for%20online%20and%20off