e%2C%20and%20preservation%20and%20techniques%20of%20germination%2C%20will%20last%20longer%20and%20plants%20from%20these%20seeds%20will%20sustain%20through%20natural%20calamities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%20300%20farmers%20in%20seed%20preservation%20techniques.%20But%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseed%20preservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20region%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20with%20him%2C%20he%20insists.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20ongoing%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Darlapudi%20Ravi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiucn.org%2Fpress-release%2F202410%2Fmore-one-three-tree-species-worldwide-faces-extinction-iucn-red-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction%20%E2%80%93%20IUCN%20Red%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20IUCN%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20October%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsii.in%2Fimportance-of-seed-banks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImportance%20of%20Seed%20Banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Federation%20of%20Seed%20Industry%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732024705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-2-1732015773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20was%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20cement%20industry%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20modern%20dietary%20practices%20lead%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20diseases.%20Here's%20how%20this%20realisation%20motivated%20him%20to%20build%20a%20seed%20bank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A72%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381089%2Fseed-preservation-andhra-pradesh-darlapudi-ravi-indigenous-local-varieties%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%2012%20Student%20Builds%20Solar-Powered%20Agro%20Vehicle%20With%20Zero%20Carbon%20Emission%20for%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Suhani%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20is%20making%20waves%20with%20a%20design%20that%20empower%20farmers%20by%20reducing%20production%20costs%20and%20boosting%20crop%20yields%2C%20helping%20them%20achieve%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20profitability%20in%20their%20farming%20practices.%20Her%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20is%20an%20innovative%2C%20solar-powered%20farming%20vehicle%20that%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20farmers%20with%20potential%20to%20cut%20down%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202%2C72%2C000%20metric%20tonnes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20was%20a%20Class%207%20student%20when%20a%20school%20field%20trip%20to%20the%20farms%20of%20Manesar%20ignited%20a%20spark%20within%20Suhani.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20the%20farmers%20toiling%20all%20day%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20sympathetic%20for%20them.%20What%20shook%20me%20the%20most%2C%20though%2C%20were%20the%20heartbreaking%20statistics%20on%20farmer%20suicides.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sight%20of%20the%20struggles%20sparked%20a%20determination%20within%20her%20to%20find%20solutions%20for%20the%20struggling%20agricultural%20community%2C%20particularly%20for%20small-scale%20farmers.%20Fuelled%20by%20a%20deep-seated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20for%20social%20ch%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%5C%22%3Eange%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20her%20receiving%20the%20prestigious%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award%2C%20a%20recognition%20bestowed%20upon%20young%20individuals%20who%20have%20made%20extraordinary%20contributions%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSwapping%20just%201%25%20of%20tractors%20with%20the%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%2C%20we%20could%20save%20an%20estimated%20Rs%20217%20million%20in%20diesel%20costs%20every%20year%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20cutting%20down%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202%2C72%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20annually%2C%20which%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20both%20economic%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287061%2Findia-indigenous-tribes-conserving-nature-forests-wildlife-environment-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmental%20sustainabi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20hr