er%20enhancing%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Suhani%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20She%20included%20a%20backup%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20used%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20or%20at%20night%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20vehicle%20remains%20functional%20even%20during%20unfavourable%20conditions.%20This%20combination%20of%20solar%20power%20and%20backup%20energy%20makes%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20a%20truly%20sustainable%20solution%20for%20farmers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20So-Apt%20is%20set%20to%20transform%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20is%20evident%20in%20her%20design.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20country%20rich%20in%20solar%20energy%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20harnessing%20this%20resource%20will%20be%20extremely%20beneficial%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20solar%20panels%20are%20designed%20to%20last%20for%20several%20years%2C%20and%20Suhani%20is%20working%20on%20increasing%20the%20energy%20reserve%20to%20make%20the%20vehicle%20even%20more%20efficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20So-Apt%20has%20been%20a%20journey%20of%20constant%20iteration%2C%20fueled%20by%20feedback%20from%20the%20farming%20community.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20to%20over%201%2C000%20farmers%2C%20shown%20them%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%2C%20and%20listened%20to%20their%20feedback.%20Through%20countless%20conversations%20and%20research%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gained%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20their%20challenges%20and%20how%20my%20vehicle%20can%20make%20a%20difference.%20The%20joy%20and%20appreciation%20I%20see%20on%20their%20faces%2C%20knowing%20that%20young%20people%20like%20me%20are%20working%20to%20help%20them%2C%20keeps%20me%20motivated%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20future%20plans%20for%20So-Apt%2C%20Suhani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20adding%20a%20GPS%20system%20to%20help%20farmers%20track%20which%20parts%20of%20their%20field%20they%20have%20covered%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20planting%2C%20irrigating%2C%20or%20applying%20fertilisers.%20This%20will%20make%20the%20farming%20process%20more%20efficient.%E2%80%9D%20She%E2%80%99s%20also%20incorporating%20a%20pH%20calculator%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20soil%20healt%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%3Eh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20further%20enhancing%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20functionality%20and%20making%20it%20an%20even%20more%20valuable%20tool%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20is%20also%20focusing%20on%20making%20the%20vehicle%20smarter%20and%20easier%20to%20use%20for%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20vehicle%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20affordable%20but%20also%20user-friendly.%20Farmers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20it%20without%20needing%20technical%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20This%20focus%20on%20simplicity%20and%20functionality%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWinning%20the%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20dedication%20and%20tireless%20effort%20have%20certainly%20not%20escaped%20attention.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20she%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20mother%20calling%20me%20and