i-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-1536x925.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-2048x1233.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-1200x723.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuhani-Chauhan-with-Honble-Prime-Minister-Shri-Narendra-Modiji-and-Honble-Minister-for-Women-and-Child-Development-Smt.-Smriti-Irani-1_11zon-1732018716-150x90.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381154%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20interaction%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20memorable%20for%20her%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interaction%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20particularly%20memorable%20for%20Suhani.%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20him%20about%20solar%20power%2C%20and%20he%20seemed%20genuinely%20excited%20about%20it.%20He%20shared%20how%20sustainability%20was%20important%20to%20him%2C%20and%20that%20really%20motivated%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suhani%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20incredible%20experience%20to%20speak%20with%20him%20about%20the%20future%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20how%20young%20people%20like%20me%20can%20contribute%20to%20this%20movement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20Suhani%E2%80%99s%20compassionate%20heart%20at%20such%20a%20tender%20age%2C%20when%20she%20felt%20for%20the%20farmers%20and%20wanted%20to%20help%20them%2C%20was%20truly%20inspiring.%20Her%20determination%20to%20turn%20her%20idea%20into%20a%20reality%2C%20from%20sketching%20prototypes%20to%20collecting%20scrap%20for%20the%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%2C%20was%20unwavering.%20As%20parents%2C%20we%20were%20privileged%20to%20witness%20her%20journey%20and%20support%20her%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20Receiving%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award%20was%20a%20surreal%20moment%2C%20a%20validation%20of%20her%20hard%20work%20and%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20youthful%20innovation%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Pooja%20Chauhan%2C%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Suhani%20is%20focused%20on%20scaling%20the%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20to%20reach%20more%20farmers%20and%20communities.%20She%20is%20currently%20in%20talks%20with%20companies%20to%20transfer%20the%20technology%20and%20bring%20the%20vehicle%20to%20market.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20So-Apt%20available%20to%20farmers%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20huge%20potential%20for%20this%20technology%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20it%20can%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20small%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20has%20learned%20a%20great%20deal%20through%20her%20journey%20with%20So-Apt%2C%20and%20she%20has%20a%20message%20for%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F378406%2Fnasscom-foundation-cisco-thingqbator-startups-mentorship-funding-solve-social-issues-using-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20innovators%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20just%20starting%20out.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20idea%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20brainstorming%20for%20So-Apt%2C%20I%20had%20so%20many%20ideas.%20Some%20of%20them%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20but%20they%20all%20helped%20me%20refine%20the%20final%20product.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20be%20afraid%20to%20experiment%20and%20explore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20we